WEBVTT

01:32.090 --> 01:34.940
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:37.940
[Episode 17]

01:42.110 --> 01:43.120
If you don't believe

01:43.120 --> 01:45.640
Yu Wanyin would say something like this
to Xie Yong'er,

01:45.640 --> 01:46.370
that's fine.

01:49.120 --> 01:51.180
I'll ask you in a different identity.

01:55.870 --> 01:56.310
How...

01:57.200 --> 01:57.640
Are...

01:58.680 --> 01:59.070
You?

02:01.030 --> 02:01.630
Answer me!

02:02.680 --> 02:03.380
How are you?

02:09.280 --> 02:10.190
You too?

02:10.710 --> 02:11.240
Yes, I am.

02:12.000 --> 02:12.630
I'm tired.

02:13.080 --> 02:14.880
Let's put our cards on the table.

02:16.620 --> 02:17.820
I don't know what you're talking about.

02:17.820 --> 02:19.690
You already know very well who I am.

02:19.690 --> 02:20.490
Stop talking!

02:20.840 --> 02:23.190
How long are you going to
keep running from this?

02:23.190 --> 02:24.870
I'll ask you that same question again
right now.

02:24.870 --> 02:26.070
Do you dare answer it?

02:28.030 --> 02:28.760
Answer what?

02:33.030 --> 02:33.829
Your Majesty.

02:34.000 --> 02:35.460
Consort Yu has gone crazy.

02:35.520 --> 02:37.380
She keeps saying strange things.

02:37.870 --> 02:39.190
I'm really scared.

02:46.310 --> 02:47.000
Is that so?

02:50.030 --> 02:51.360
Let me answer it for you.

02:56.079 --> 02:56.630
Fine.

02:59.120 --> 02:59.840
Thank you.

03:03.910 --> 03:04.870
And you?

03:07.710 --> 03:08.280
You too?

03:17.340 --> 03:20.600
[Kunyu Palace]

03:27.630 --> 03:28.560
Why are you here?

03:28.960 --> 03:31.000
Is everything with the envoy delegation
settled?

03:31.000 --> 03:31.750
More or less.

03:32.360 --> 03:34.960
I muddled through it
without any real trouble.

03:35.590 --> 03:36.190
I heard

03:36.590 --> 03:38.850
the Empress Dowager gave you a hard time.

03:39.310 --> 03:41.440
I managed to muddle through it as well.

03:42.800 --> 03:43.600
You're awake.

03:51.150 --> 03:52.400
So you two, like me,

03:52.800 --> 03:53.910
are also transmigrators?

03:53.910 --> 03:54.240
Yes.

03:55.100 --> 03:56.190
Since we're all the same kind...

03:56.190 --> 03:57.850
Since we're all the same kind,

03:57.910 --> 03:59.640
why didn't you tell me earlier?

04:00.080 --> 04:01.240
Did you have to watch me from the shadows

04:01.240 --> 04:02.800
and see me make a fool of myself?

04:02.800 --> 04:03.240
Right.

04:04.910 --> 04:07.110
Watching you cheat on me the whole time—

04:07.400 --> 04:08.470
pretty thrilling.

04:11.360 --> 04:11.820
Then...

04:12.560 --> 04:14.290
Then why are you telling me now?

04:14.470 --> 04:15.600
Why not just kill me?

04:16.120 --> 04:19.040
Just tell the public that Xie Yong'er
died from childbirth complications.

04:19.040 --> 04:20.920
This way, Prince Duan
wouldn't suspect anything.

04:20.920 --> 04:22.270
Wouldn't that be even better?

04:22.270 --> 04:22.830
Indeed.

04:23.920 --> 04:25.520
Wanyin, why did you tell her?

04:27.360 --> 04:28.040
Well...

04:28.580 --> 04:29.780
Why not just kill her?

04:35.159 --> 04:35.930
Yong'er,

04:36.200 --> 04:36.700
look,

04:37.390 --> 04:40.050
we've already reached the point of
miscarriage

04:40.680 --> 04:42.220
and framing each other.

04:42.510 --> 04:43.490
If the plot keeps developing like this,

04:43.490 --> 04:45.090
it'll be a fight to the death.

04:45.950 --> 04:47.610
Since we're all the same kind,

04:47.800 --> 04:50.060
isn't there another possibility for us?

04:50.390 --> 04:51.990
Stop being so hypocritical.

04:53.040 --> 04:56.040
You never intended to tell me the truth
from the start.

04:56.390 --> 04:57.390
Now that you see me

04:57.430 --> 04:58.230
in this state,

04:59.430 --> 05:01.480
you come telling me we're the same kind?

05:01.480 --> 05:03.740
Haven't you had your fill of the joke yet?

05:04.800 --> 05:07.460
If we had told you
right after we transmigrated,

05:07.560 --> 05:08.750
would your first reaction

05:08.750 --> 05:10.080
have been to cooperate?

05:12.070 --> 05:14.480
At that time, you had already
sided with Prince Duan.

05:14.480 --> 05:16.880
Suddenly finding out
that I was a wild card,

05:16.950 --> 05:18.950
you'd probably
have gone straight to Prince Duan

05:18.950 --> 05:19.610
and told him

05:20.240 --> 05:22.490
to take me out

05:22.630 --> 05:23.890
while I was still weak.

05:24.830 --> 05:25.600
Am I wrong?

05:28.600 --> 05:29.360
Makes sense.

05:31.750 --> 05:32.110
But

05:33.360 --> 05:35.360
is there anything wrong with
me wanting to survive?

05:35.360 --> 05:36.830
Don't you two want to survive?

05:36.830 --> 05:38.040
Of course we do.

05:38.720 --> 05:39.250
Yong'er.

05:39.870 --> 05:41.390
I don't think you're wrong.

05:41.390 --> 05:43.560
It's this darn situation that's wrong.

05:43.560 --> 05:44.430
If possible,

05:45.390 --> 05:46.720
I hope you, me,

05:47.630 --> 05:48.430
the three of us

05:48.600 --> 05:50.000
can all make it to the end.

05:50.240 --> 05:51.120
Then we

05:51.630 --> 05:53.030
can have hotpot together

05:53.040 --> 05:54.159
and play a few rounds of
"Fight the Landlord."

05:54.159 --> 05:55.420
It would be so much fun.

05:55.870 --> 05:56.930
Stop with your act.

05:59.950 --> 06:01.480
If the roles were reversed,

06:02.160 --> 06:03.530
I believe your choices

06:04.120 --> 06:06.180
wouldn't be any different from mine.

06:07.310 --> 06:08.840
But the difference is huge.

06:10.800 --> 06:12.390
If Wanyin had been as ruthless

06:12.390 --> 06:14.120
as you were when you framed her,

06:14.510 --> 06:16.240
you wouldn't even be alive now.

06:20.360 --> 06:21.510
Come on, bro.

06:22.160 --> 06:24.420
Are you determined to sabotage our plan?

06:25.750 --> 06:27.210
That's not the case at all.

06:27.560 --> 06:28.620
Actually, Yong'er

06:28.630 --> 06:30.290
is not as cruel as he imagined.

06:31.240 --> 06:32.170
Right, Yong'er?

06:35.680 --> 06:37.810
Come on, get up. It's cold on the floor.

06:40.950 --> 06:42.010
What are you doing?

06:42.159 --> 06:42.890
I don't think

06:43.159 --> 06:44.750
there's anything more
to talk about with her.

06:44.750 --> 06:45.280
Let's go.

06:56.070 --> 06:58.480
Why were you constantly
undermining my efforts just now?

06:58.480 --> 07:00.870
Xie Yong'er is emotionally vulnerable
right now.

07:00.870 --> 07:02.200
I was trying to turn her.

07:02.360 --> 07:02.830
I know.

07:03.430 --> 07:04.690
I was working with you.

07:04.870 --> 07:06.600
What kind of "working with me" is that?

07:06.600 --> 07:07.430
I intimidate,

07:07.800 --> 07:08.480
you entice.

07:11.720 --> 07:13.070
She cheated on me, all right?

07:13.070 --> 07:15.480
Even if I was just putting on a show
for the Empress Dowager,

07:15.480 --> 07:18.210
it's reasonable for me to be
a little harsh on her.

07:18.830 --> 07:20.490
Xie Yong'er is a real villain.

07:21.120 --> 07:22.580
Forget about turning her.

07:22.630 --> 07:24.360
Do people who've made mistakes

07:25.070 --> 07:26.800
not deserve a fresh start?

07:30.680 --> 07:33.140
She probably didn't intend to
harm me today.

07:34.070 --> 07:37.000
It was just a stress response to
the Empress Dowager.

07:37.070 --> 07:39.360
I just happened to
have a higher ground than her,

07:39.360 --> 07:40.120
and I met you,

07:41.240 --> 07:43.500
which allowed me to seize the initiative

07:44.070 --> 07:46.670
and even appear justified
in everything I did.

07:47.630 --> 07:50.090
Everything I did was just
to protect myself.

07:50.870 --> 07:52.870
The only reason I wanted her to survive

07:52.870 --> 07:55.870
was because I'm worried
the story would get cut short.

07:56.830 --> 08:00.160
So essentially, I'm not really
any different from her, am I?

08:00.480 --> 08:00.940
You are.

08:06.000 --> 08:07.390
Have you never thought

08:08.270 --> 08:09.800
that keeping someone alive

08:10.070 --> 08:11.400
can be done in many ways?

08:16.560 --> 08:17.560
Chop off her legs,

08:18.390 --> 08:19.650
imprison her for life—

08:20.600 --> 08:22.060
so long as she doesn't die,

08:22.600 --> 08:23.070
the goal

08:23.920 --> 08:25.520
is still achieved, isn't it?

08:28.480 --> 08:30.080
You can't even think of that,

08:30.160 --> 08:32.220
and you dare call yourself a villain?

08:32.960 --> 08:35.890
If it were Xie Yong'er,
she'd definitely think of it.

08:37.720 --> 08:39.179
She's just a 2D character.

08:40.320 --> 08:41.320
She's as wicked

08:42.440 --> 08:44.100
as the plot requires her to be.

08:46.080 --> 08:46.480
You...

08:46.960 --> 08:47.760
What's wrong?

08:51.910 --> 08:52.440
Nothing.

08:57.720 --> 09:00.320
Wanyin, you left in a hurry.
Did you eat enough?

09:00.910 --> 09:01.910
I'm okay.

09:02.840 --> 09:04.030
I'll just ask the servants

09:04.030 --> 09:06.830
to heat up something
for a late-night snack later.

09:19.080 --> 09:20.540
That's thoughtful of you.

09:21.630 --> 09:23.120
Dealing with the Empress Dowager,

09:23.120 --> 09:24.550
guarding against the Yan State envoys,

09:24.550 --> 09:26.750
and still remembering to bring me food.

09:35.510 --> 09:36.030
No way.

09:37.790 --> 09:39.190
Getting moved so easily,

09:40.480 --> 09:41.480
"great villain"?

09:47.600 --> 09:49.460
All right, I'll stop teasing you.

09:49.550 --> 09:51.950
Eat up, or I'll have brought it
for nothing.

09:58.870 --> 09:59.600
By the way,

10:00.360 --> 10:02.360
what kind of person were you before?

10:04.190 --> 10:05.390
Just an ordinary guy.

10:05.840 --> 10:07.640
No real skills, no connections,

10:08.510 --> 10:10.150
and... Okay-looking, I guess.

10:10.150 --> 10:11.010
So modest, huh?

10:12.390 --> 10:13.250
What about you?

10:13.870 --> 10:14.240
Me?

10:15.550 --> 10:16.970
I was also ordinary.

10:17.270 --> 10:18.910
Working nine to five every day,

10:18.910 --> 10:20.840
serving one client after another.

10:21.440 --> 10:22.270
When it got busy,

10:22.270 --> 10:24.400
I didn't even have time to wash my hair—

10:25.600 --> 10:27.930
completely different from how I look now.

10:39.750 --> 10:41.350
No need to put yourself down.

10:43.000 --> 10:45.260
You must have been good-looking as well.

11:02.150 --> 11:03.080
Are you alright?

11:03.200 --> 11:03.730
I'm fine.

11:06.270 --> 11:06.910
Well,

11:07.390 --> 11:08.960
I'll head back to the palace first.

11:08.960 --> 11:13.760
Aren't we still putting on that whole
"chasing-your-wife-after-screwing-up" act?

11:15.510 --> 11:16.640
Get some rest early.

11:38.160 --> 11:39.600
As soon as the banquet ended,

11:39.600 --> 11:42.080
His Majesty immediately
went to Consort Xie's place

11:42.080 --> 11:44.390
and tightened the security
around her chambers.

11:44.390 --> 11:45.450
From what I can see,

11:46.240 --> 11:48.240
His Majesty is quite attentive to her.

11:48.240 --> 11:50.840
It doesn't look like he was
the one behind this.

11:52.240 --> 11:53.130
Then this

11:53.960 --> 11:55.270
really is suspicious.

11:56.600 --> 11:57.240
Could it be

11:58.120 --> 11:59.510
that I overthought it?

12:02.150 --> 12:03.150
You may leave now.

12:04.080 --> 12:04.510
Yes.

12:10.080 --> 12:10.880
Your Majesty.

12:11.120 --> 12:13.440
His Majesty has always kept out of
state affairs.

12:13.440 --> 12:14.480
Why is it that this time, he repeatedly

12:14.480 --> 12:16.670
stepped in to smooth things over
for the envoy delegation?

12:16.670 --> 12:17.240
We

12:17.790 --> 12:19.600
truly cannot make sense of it.

12:21.440 --> 12:23.790
It seems His Majesty's wings
have grown stronger

12:23.790 --> 12:25.920
and he's begun to form ideas of his own.

12:27.200 --> 12:28.660
If the peace talks succeed

12:29.150 --> 12:30.750
and the borders are secured,

12:31.670 --> 12:32.790
Prince Duan's power

12:32.790 --> 12:34.120
will swell completely,

12:34.670 --> 12:36.530
and we'll be left on the back foot.

12:38.750 --> 12:40.010
So what do you suggest?

12:42.240 --> 12:43.700
His Highness Crown Prince

12:44.120 --> 12:45.870
is wise and benevolent,

12:47.030 --> 12:49.360
and he carries the bearing of
a wise ruler.

13:00.510 --> 13:02.240
These Yan people can't even

13:03.120 --> 13:06.960
manage a proper sentence
in the official tongue.

13:07.910 --> 13:09.750
Walking around the capital,

13:10.320 --> 13:13.390
frictions with the Xia people
are bound to happen.

13:14.320 --> 13:15.960
A bunch of barbarians—

13:17.320 --> 13:18.910
one wrong word

13:19.200 --> 13:21.910
and they might start throwing punches.

13:23.390 --> 13:24.960
Blades have no eyes.

13:25.550 --> 13:26.610
Before you know it,

13:27.440 --> 13:29.030
there could be bloodshed.

13:30.390 --> 13:31.830
I'll see to it right away.

13:36.480 --> 13:37.280
Your Majesty.

13:37.840 --> 13:40.000
Killing envoys during a conflict
between two states

13:40.000 --> 13:41.730
could very well spark a new war.

13:42.270 --> 13:43.870
That's right, Your Majesty.

13:44.480 --> 13:45.940
The safety of our state

13:46.120 --> 13:49.320
is something we officials
cannot afford not to consider.

13:49.440 --> 13:51.000
What's there to worry about?

13:51.000 --> 13:52.670
Even if the Central Army is defeated,

13:52.670 --> 13:55.200
we can still deploy
the Left and Right Armies.

13:55.360 --> 13:56.270
Then we can just sit back and

13:56.270 --> 13:59.850
watch the Yan people and Prince Duan
wear each other out.

13:59.960 --> 14:00.360
But...

14:03.670 --> 14:04.470
Crown Prince.

14:05.440 --> 14:06.850
What's your take on this?

14:10.960 --> 14:12.270
If Grandmother believes we should fight,

14:12.270 --> 14:13.470
then we should fight.

14:19.790 --> 14:20.320
Exactly!

14:21.510 --> 14:23.270
If the Crown Prince says
we fight,

14:23.270 --> 14:24.300
then we fight!

14:27.030 --> 14:28.480
Thanks to you, Yang,

14:28.510 --> 14:30.000
that I get to enjoy such fine wine today.

14:30.000 --> 14:31.480
I won't stand on ceremony then.

14:31.480 --> 14:31.940
Come on.

14:32.000 --> 14:34.480
It's rare to see you
drinking so heartily, Li.

14:34.480 --> 14:35.280
I'll join you.

14:35.600 --> 14:37.000
It's been ages since the three of us
got together.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.000
Why are you drinking tea?

14:38.000 --> 14:38.860
Switch to wine.

14:39.670 --> 14:40.440
I'll pass.

14:40.790 --> 14:43.650
I'd like to stay alive a bit longer
to tend my fields.

14:45.390 --> 14:46.750
Don't drink alone.
Come on, let's drink together.

14:46.750 --> 14:47.680
Come on. Cheers.

14:53.790 --> 14:55.240
Yang, since you got here,

14:55.270 --> 14:57.000
you've barely said a few words.

14:57.120 --> 14:59.000
Aren't you usually the chattiest one?

14:59.000 --> 15:00.060
Why so quiet today?

15:01.670 --> 15:03.840
You seem to have lost weight, Yang.

15:04.240 --> 15:05.640
Has something happened?

15:08.870 --> 15:11.670
I never want to talk again
in this lifetime.

15:17.200 --> 15:17.840
You two

15:18.390 --> 15:19.990
both got what you wished for—

15:20.790 --> 15:22.790
you joined the Ministry of Revenue,

15:23.000 --> 15:25.120
and you get to keep studying farming.

15:27.120 --> 15:29.670
Do you know what I'm in charge of

15:29.670 --> 15:32.070
after entering the Imperial Observatory?

15:33.270 --> 15:34.360
Divination.

15:36.840 --> 15:39.790
Reading the stars for omens of
fortune and disaster, rise and fall.

15:39.790 --> 15:42.630
I spend my days spinning stories
for people.

15:45.910 --> 15:47.910
And you think I can just make them up?

15:48.720 --> 15:49.510
No.

15:52.200 --> 15:55.630
If His Majesty wants this reading
to foretell misfortune,

15:57.080 --> 15:58.840
then I have to couch it
in grand, arcane phrasing—

15:58.840 --> 16:01.240
pacing the constellations,
plumbing the mysteries of change—

16:01.240 --> 16:04.600
so that even bad news
sounds ornate and eloquent.

16:06.870 --> 16:09.600
Is my literary talent
really meant for this?

16:22.390 --> 16:23.250
Let them leave.

16:23.360 --> 16:24.620
Enough with the dance.

16:24.910 --> 16:25.370
You all,

16:25.700 --> 16:26.240
get out.

16:27.240 --> 16:28.090
Get out.

16:28.790 --> 16:30.050
All of you, get out too.

16:31.200 --> 16:32.080
-Let's go then.
-Let's go.

16:32.080 --> 16:32.610
Hurry up.

16:33.870 --> 16:35.800
What kind of rubbish dance is that?

16:35.960 --> 16:38.760
Nowhere near as good as
the dances of our Great Yan.

16:39.150 --> 16:40.320
And this wine and these dishes—

16:40.320 --> 16:41.170
too delicate.

16:41.720 --> 16:42.980
Not satisfying at all!

16:43.080 --> 16:44.670
Ever since we came to Great Xia,

16:44.670 --> 16:46.080
I haven't felt at ease for a single day!

16:46.080 --> 16:47.360
At the Grand Longevity Banquet,

16:47.360 --> 16:49.910
the Empress Dowager
was clearly targeting us.

16:49.910 --> 16:50.600
I just can't

16:51.120 --> 16:52.320
swallow such insult!

16:52.790 --> 16:53.360
Enough.

16:55.840 --> 16:57.330
We've long known

16:58.200 --> 17:00.730
how insidious and cunning
the Xia people are.

17:01.550 --> 17:03.010
What's most important now

17:03.840 --> 17:05.240
is keeping our composure

17:05.790 --> 17:07.650
and waiting for the right moment.

17:08.109 --> 17:10.569
As long as Xiahou Dan agrees to
meet us alone,

17:11.240 --> 17:13.119
we can kill this dog of an emperor

17:14.160 --> 17:16.020
without losing a single soldier.

17:19.640 --> 17:21.200
That old Emperor of Yan

17:21.200 --> 17:23.069
is counting his chickens too early.

17:23.069 --> 17:24.359
Let's put in some effort

17:24.359 --> 17:26.220
and make sure he spends his old age

17:26.790 --> 17:29.120
thoroughly engulfed in the flames of war.

17:29.960 --> 17:31.020
Speaking of which,

17:31.920 --> 17:33.860
we pulled a switcheroo

17:34.160 --> 17:36.620
and took
the real envoy delegation's place.

17:37.480 --> 17:38.140
Do you think

17:39.030 --> 17:40.410
Zhaluowahan

17:41.110 --> 17:42.510
has realized by now?

17:43.030 --> 17:44.070
And what if he has?

17:44.750 --> 17:45.680
He's nothing but

17:46.110 --> 17:47.580
a toothless old wolf now.

17:48.830 --> 17:52.540
He's probably eagerly waiting for
the outcome of the peace talks.

17:55.960 --> 17:56.490
Alright.

17:57.960 --> 17:58.400
Come on.

17:58.400 --> 17:58.750
Cheers.

17:58.750 --> 17:59.280
Alright.

17:59.830 --> 18:01.520
It's time for the Xia people

18:02.200 --> 18:04.000
to pay the blood debt they owe us.

18:04.350 --> 18:05.880
I, Yang Duojie,

18:06.750 --> 18:10.680
with my ten years of diligent study
and exceptional talent,

18:10.680 --> 18:13.280
actually ended up
becoming a fortune-teller.

18:13.790 --> 18:15.050
Keep your voices down.

18:16.550 --> 18:16.960
Yang.

18:20.590 --> 18:21.240
Yang.

18:22.030 --> 18:23.310
Didn't His Majesty say

18:23.880 --> 18:24.720
that, for now, he needs you to write

18:24.720 --> 18:27.160
those mystical, mumbo-jumbo pieces
to fool people,

18:27.160 --> 18:29.820
and he'll transfer you elsewhere
after a while?

18:32.590 --> 18:35.320
Allow me to say something
downright treasonous—

18:36.110 --> 18:37.240
do you believe that?

18:37.960 --> 18:38.480
I do.

18:39.830 --> 18:40.760
I believe it too.

18:42.480 --> 18:43.200
Therefore,

18:44.110 --> 18:45.270
you should also have

18:45.830 --> 18:47.270
more faith in His Majesty.

18:47.270 --> 18:48.310
His Majesty also told me

18:48.310 --> 18:51.480
to keep compiling the land registers
from various regions,

18:51.480 --> 18:53.070
saying they would be useful someday.

18:53.070 --> 18:55.870
That counts as the Emperor's promise,
doesn't it?

18:56.480 --> 19:00.410
That's not what you said when you
first joined the Ministry of Revenue.

19:00.940 --> 19:04.130
So you don't mind
Er Lan being so socially adept

19:04.160 --> 19:06.070
and rising through the ranks with ease
anymore?

19:06.070 --> 19:07.600
I don't see him that way now.

19:08.830 --> 19:11.510
Then why didn't you invite Er
along today?

19:12.070 --> 19:13.830
You're the host—
shouldn't you be the one to invite him?

19:13.830 --> 19:15.480
But you both work in
the Ministry of Revenue.

19:15.480 --> 19:16.920
Yes, we do.

19:16.920 --> 19:18.510
I even nodded to him
when I saw him earlier.

19:18.510 --> 19:20.170
I thought he was heading here.

19:20.510 --> 19:21.640
That's on you.

19:22.550 --> 19:24.830
Besides, he's probably swamped with
work now. Able men are always busy, right?

19:24.830 --> 19:28.290
How would he have time to come out
for our little get-together?

19:28.800 --> 19:30.930
Well said—"able men are always busy."

19:33.030 --> 19:35.030
You're all so steadfast.

19:36.680 --> 19:39.200
Turns out I'm the only one still wavering.

19:44.720 --> 19:46.320
Take Wang Zhao for instance.

19:46.960 --> 19:49.510
He was supposed to return
with the envoy delegation,

19:49.510 --> 19:51.440
yet now he's been kept in Yan State.

19:53.720 --> 19:55.350
I fear the worst for him.

19:57.160 --> 20:00.030
And His Majesty, fully aware that
the Yan people came with ill intent,

20:00.030 --> 20:02.690
still lowered himself
to curry favor with them.

20:03.270 --> 20:06.110
I can't understand
what he's really thinking,

20:06.880 --> 20:07.790
and I don't know

20:07.790 --> 20:09.350
-what he takes us for...
-Stop there!

20:09.350 --> 20:10.440
-What's happening?
-What do you want?

20:10.440 --> 20:11.310
They're from the Yan State, right?

20:11.310 --> 20:14.270
-You haven't paid yet. You can't leave.
-Looks like it's those Yan fellows.

20:14.270 --> 20:15.750
Speak of the devil.

20:16.230 --> 20:17.890
Six dishes, four jugs of wine—

20:18.440 --> 20:20.440
you even gave us two coins in change.

20:21.590 --> 20:23.650
That only covers the food and drinks.

20:23.790 --> 20:25.800
You didn't pay for the songstress.

20:26.160 --> 20:27.160
What songstress?

20:27.680 --> 20:29.340
She came in and sang on her own,

20:29.790 --> 20:31.120
and she barely sang a couple of lines

20:31.120 --> 20:32.400
before we sent her away.

20:32.400 --> 20:33.530
Everyone knows that

20:34.000 --> 20:36.390
Miss Miaoying is a star on our street.

20:36.830 --> 20:39.350
So many people spend a fortune
to hire her, yet can't.

20:39.350 --> 20:41.430
How is it that with you Yan folks,

20:41.600 --> 20:43.730
she came performing for you on her own?

20:51.610 --> 20:52.740
How much do you want?

20:52.880 --> 20:54.680
You're quite straightforward.

20:54.790 --> 20:55.450
50 taels.

20:57.680 --> 20:59.680
They're deliberately giving us trouble.

20:59.680 --> 21:01.020
We can't pay this money.

21:03.160 --> 21:05.290
Don't forget the purpose of this trip.

21:05.400 --> 21:08.130
We can't risk the big picture
over small matters.

21:12.350 --> 21:13.440
That should be enough.

21:13.440 --> 21:14.370
It's not enough!

21:16.400 --> 21:18.110
This isn't just a matter of money!

21:18.110 --> 21:21.200
They... They even tried to
take advantage of me.

21:21.200 --> 21:22.310
That's pure slander!

21:22.310 --> 21:23.920
Who tried to take advantage of you?

21:23.920 --> 21:25.270
Him! It was him!

21:25.350 --> 21:25.680
Me?

21:25.830 --> 21:26.690
Yes, it was him!

21:26.720 --> 21:27.650
Everyone, look!

21:27.750 --> 21:28.720
He even left his handprint right here!

21:28.720 --> 21:30.160
-You don't think this situation...
-I didn't take advantage of her!

21:30.160 --> 21:31.440
Is going to escalate into a fight, do you?

21:31.440 --> 21:32.830
Don't jinx it. Just stop talking.

21:32.830 --> 21:33.430
It was him!

21:34.880 --> 21:35.720
-How could you hit her?
-Let's go.

21:35.720 --> 21:36.920
How could you do that?

21:36.960 --> 21:37.620
Stop there!

21:42.110 --> 21:44.680
Brother, they're the ones who bullied me!

21:44.880 --> 21:46.080
You bullied my sister

21:46.480 --> 21:48.160
and think you can just walk away?

21:48.160 --> 21:48.760
Beat them!

21:56.000 --> 21:57.060
We can't kill them.

21:58.310 --> 21:58.920
But, Your Highness...

21:58.920 --> 22:00.640
If we kill them, we'll be charged

22:00.640 --> 22:01.440
and arrested.

22:06.640 --> 22:07.790
Something's not right.

22:07.790 --> 22:09.200
These people's fighting skills

22:09.200 --> 22:11.750
don't seem like those of
ordinary laborers or commoners.

22:11.750 --> 22:12.480
You go first.

22:12.790 --> 22:13.880
We'll stay here and deal with them.

22:13.880 --> 22:14.310
No.

22:15.510 --> 22:16.840
We must leave together.

22:30.720 --> 22:31.160
Who was it?

22:30.800 --> 22:31.820
[Zuixiang House]

22:32.150 --> 22:32.700
Run!

22:34.750 --> 22:35.120
Run!

22:36.400 --> 22:37.330
Are you crazy?

22:37.680 --> 22:39.530
Do you know how much
that jug of wine is worth?

22:39.530 --> 22:40.510
You're the crazy one!

22:40.510 --> 22:41.720
At this point, you still care about money?

22:41.720 --> 22:43.000
Stop arguing, you two.

22:43.240 --> 22:44.840
They clearly came prepared.

22:44.960 --> 22:47.000
Who knows
if they're the Empress Dowager's people.

22:47.000 --> 22:48.030
Here's what we'll do. Yang,

22:48.030 --> 22:50.270
hurry into the palace
and report this to His Majesty.

22:50.270 --> 22:51.480
Li, let's follow them

22:51.550 --> 22:52.880
and see if we can help.

22:52.960 --> 22:54.560
Follow them? I just hit them.

22:54.750 --> 22:56.510
They don't know it was you.

22:57.000 --> 22:57.680
Besides,

22:57.680 --> 22:59.960
the envoy delegation's safety
is crucial to stopping the war.

22:59.960 --> 23:00.820
Let's split up.

23:01.000 --> 23:01.750
You're right.

23:01.750 --> 23:02.240
Yang!

23:03.680 --> 23:04.210
This way.

23:04.790 --> 23:06.990
Do we have to sneak around like thieves?

23:08.550 --> 23:09.070
Stop!

23:10.400 --> 23:11.060
Stop there!

23:13.510 --> 23:14.270
Block them!

23:24.710 --> 23:26.440
There's a path behind the wall.

23:26.720 --> 23:27.400
Climb over!

23:27.480 --> 23:27.850
Okay.

23:37.880 --> 23:38.410
Let's go!

23:41.960 --> 23:43.130
Stop! Don't run!

23:44.000 --> 23:44.800
Get down here!

23:47.830 --> 23:48.110
Easy!

23:48.110 --> 23:49.110
Behave yourself!

23:50.750 --> 23:51.130
Move!

24:00.880 --> 24:02.880
Thank you for the timely report, Mr. Li.

24:02.880 --> 24:06.210
We'll take these criminals back
for thorough questioning.

24:10.310 --> 24:12.030
Those Yan State envoys

24:12.790 --> 24:14.190
should have left safely.

24:16.030 --> 24:17.710
They actually dared carry out

24:17.830 --> 24:19.750
such bandit-like attacks
in broad daylight.

24:19.750 --> 24:20.240
It seems

24:20.880 --> 24:22.750
the Empress Dowager is really going to
show her real colors.

24:22.750 --> 24:24.480
The crisis in these peace talks

24:24.750 --> 24:25.950
is still unresolved.

24:27.550 --> 24:30.410
Let's hope His Majesty
can make preparations soon.

24:37.510 --> 24:38.440
Where's Hawugu?

24:45.400 --> 24:47.110
Those people who came to kill us

24:47.110 --> 24:49.510
must have been sent by
the Empress Dowager.

24:50.110 --> 24:52.570
That woman targeted me
back in the main hall.

24:52.640 --> 24:54.720
I suppose she couldn't think of
any other tricks.

24:54.720 --> 24:56.830
Those soldiers arrived pretty fast though.

24:56.830 --> 24:58.680
It was probably the person
who threw the jug

24:58.680 --> 25:00.200
who notified the soldiers.

25:00.200 --> 25:01.860
Could it be the Emperor's men?

25:02.480 --> 25:03.140
Not likely.

25:03.750 --> 25:04.480
I don't think

25:05.510 --> 25:06.540
they're with the same group as

25:06.540 --> 25:08.870
the ones who told us to
climb over the wall.

25:09.270 --> 25:12.070
So there's internal conflict in Great Xia
as well.

25:13.550 --> 25:14.080
Let's go.

25:19.640 --> 25:21.700
I left right after giving the signal.

25:21.830 --> 25:23.160
As Your Highness instructed,

25:23.160 --> 25:26.160
I didn't show my face in front of
the envoy delegation.

25:26.830 --> 25:28.440
Did you discover anything else?

25:28.440 --> 25:30.040
That Haqina in their group

25:30.880 --> 25:33.160
doesn't seem to be the real leader.

25:34.270 --> 25:35.270
During the fight,

25:35.790 --> 25:38.850
I heard him call that burly attendant
"Your Highness."

25:39.880 --> 25:42.820
I also found that bearded man
very suspicious.

25:43.640 --> 25:45.640
He seemed to be deliberately disguised,

25:45.640 --> 25:48.030
and he kept reminding those around him

25:48.050 --> 25:49.510
not to provoke conflicts.

25:50.510 --> 25:51.370
I remember now.

25:52.200 --> 25:53.930
There was indeed such a person.

25:55.680 --> 25:57.200
At the Grand Longevity Banquet,

25:57.200 --> 25:58.850
you said he was a master fighter,
right, Mr. Bei?

25:58.850 --> 25:59.650
That's right.

25:59.720 --> 26:01.640
That man's internal force
is extremely profound,

26:01.640 --> 26:03.100
far superior to Haqina's.

26:03.720 --> 26:05.050
So here's the question:

26:06.350 --> 26:07.810
why would a master fighter

26:08.420 --> 26:10.350
disguise himself as an attendant?

26:10.790 --> 26:11.830
Those Yan people

26:13.000 --> 26:14.000
have probably never

26:14.000 --> 26:16.730
been truly seen by
our Great Xia's people before.

26:17.350 --> 26:20.610
There's supposed to be no need for them
to hide their faces.

26:20.750 --> 26:22.080
Since he's in disguise,

26:22.830 --> 26:24.690
he must be someone familiar to us.

26:24.920 --> 26:28.400
The occasion where our people
would recognize his face...

26:29.590 --> 26:30.920
Could it be...

26:31.960 --> 26:32.960
The battlefield?

26:33.270 --> 26:34.310
With his skills,

26:35.350 --> 26:39.010
he could indeed live up to the title of
top fighter of the Yan State.

26:39.270 --> 26:40.200
He's Tu'er!

26:40.730 --> 26:43.650
[Prince Tu'er]

26:41.190 --> 26:43.630
With the beard, they do look

26:44.200 --> 26:45.680
about 70% to 80% similar.

26:46.200 --> 26:47.400
But it's long been rumored that

26:47.400 --> 26:49.350
Tu'er and the old Emperor of Yan
are at odds.

26:49.350 --> 26:51.880
So how could he have been sent
as part of the envoy delegation?

26:51.880 --> 26:52.680
Could it be...

26:52.880 --> 26:54.030
The envoy delegation is fake.

26:54.030 --> 26:54.960
No wonder!

26:55.400 --> 26:57.480
No wonder Wang Zhao
didn't come back with them.

26:57.480 --> 26:58.280
Your Majesty,

26:58.720 --> 27:01.030
they must be carrying many schemes
on this visit.

27:01.030 --> 27:03.290
Please be extra cautious, Your Majesty.

27:03.590 --> 27:04.390
I understand.

27:08.270 --> 27:09.400
Here's what we'll do.

27:09.400 --> 27:09.930
Mr. Yang.

27:10.030 --> 27:10.680
Yes, Your Majesty.

27:10.680 --> 27:14.310
Send the Ministry of Rites to
the envoy delegation's inn to apologize.

27:14.310 --> 27:15.590
The more ceremonious the display,
the better.

27:15.590 --> 27:16.250
Apologize?

27:16.790 --> 27:17.920
But shouldn't we...

27:21.440 --> 27:22.500
Yes, Your Majesty.

27:27.510 --> 27:28.000
Dan.

27:28.350 --> 27:30.510
Those Yan people have not come
with good intentions.

27:30.510 --> 27:32.570
You should make preparations early.

27:33.200 --> 27:34.460
If we want peace talks,

27:35.070 --> 27:36.270
we have to take risks.

27:37.790 --> 27:38.880
Besides, in a way,

27:40.160 --> 27:42.160
Tu'er and I should have met long ago.

27:42.400 --> 27:43.380
Then should we

27:43.790 --> 27:45.520
tell Wanyin about this matter?

27:45.640 --> 27:46.000
No.

27:48.680 --> 27:50.210
The matter with Xie Yong'er

27:50.440 --> 27:52.240
is already troubling her enough.

27:52.240 --> 27:54.440
I don't want to add more pressure on her.

27:56.030 --> 27:57.150
[Prince Tu'er]

27:57.150 --> 28:01.430
[Beautiful Lady Shanyi]

28:02.340 --> 28:05.300
[A few years ago]

28:34.960 --> 28:41.340
[Yixuan Restaurant]

28:46.550 --> 28:48.950
This is a gift sent by
the Great Xia Emperor,

28:50.270 --> 28:52.110
saying it's compensation
to our envoy delegation

28:52.110 --> 28:53.970
for what happened during the day.

28:56.550 --> 28:58.040
All they know

28:58.590 --> 28:59.720
is how to apologize.

29:01.000 --> 29:03.550
I noticed there are more guards
on duty today.

29:04.110 --> 29:06.440
It's said they were specially reinforced

29:06.480 --> 29:08.920
to prevent the criminals
from striking again—

29:08.920 --> 29:10.120
to protect us.

29:11.750 --> 29:13.810
Whether they're trying to protect us

29:14.160 --> 29:15.570
or keep an eye on us

29:16.640 --> 29:17.510
is hard to say.

29:20.240 --> 29:21.530
You know, years ago,

29:22.070 --> 29:24.680
when the Emperor of Yan
fought against our country,

29:24.680 --> 29:26.600
he didn't just get shot in one eye—

29:26.720 --> 29:29.510
he was actually hit in another part
of his body as well.

29:29.510 --> 29:31.850
That's why he has no children of his own

29:32.070 --> 29:34.050
and only has Tu'er as his nephew.

29:34.920 --> 29:38.120
Zhaluowahan may not have been
especially close to Tu'er,

29:38.550 --> 29:41.480
but he dutifully taught him
how to ride and hunt.

29:42.480 --> 29:43.740
Who would have thought

29:44.070 --> 29:46.800
those two had such affection
as uncle and nephew?

29:47.720 --> 29:50.920
In the blink of an eye,
Tu'er grew into a valiant young man,

29:50.960 --> 29:53.550
surpassing the Emperor of Yan
in riding and archery,

29:53.550 --> 29:56.880
and the number of subjects supporting him
gradually increased.

29:56.880 --> 29:59.530
As Tu'er became the Yan State's
top fighter,

29:59.790 --> 30:01.310
calls for the old Emperor of Yan
to abdicate

30:01.310 --> 30:02.840
and give the throne to Tu'er

30:02.960 --> 30:04.680
grew louder by the day.

30:07.920 --> 30:11.380
Truly, raising a nephew
turned out to be the uncle's hardship.

30:13.790 --> 30:16.750
Beautiful Lady Shanyi
was originally Tu'er's lover,

30:16.750 --> 30:19.750
but was sent to Great Xia
as a gift by the Emperor of Yan.

30:19.880 --> 30:23.000
She later died in the palace
after a failed assassination attempt.

30:23.000 --> 30:24.750
However, afterward, the Yan people

30:24.750 --> 30:26.680
not only denied the assassination attempt,

30:26.680 --> 30:28.940
but even accused Great Xia of killing her

30:29.270 --> 30:32.000
and used this as an excuse
to wage war against us.

30:32.750 --> 30:36.300
So Tu'er must hate the Emperor to death.

30:36.440 --> 30:37.270
This time,

30:38.030 --> 30:40.460
could he be trying to imitate Jing Ke,

30:40.960 --> 30:44.240
changing his name and disguising himself
to infiltrate the envoy delegation?

30:44.240 --> 30:45.960
Risking his life seems unnecessary.

30:45.960 --> 30:48.160
The Emperor is already in a weak position,

30:48.160 --> 30:50.060
and the expert by his side is dead.

30:50.960 --> 30:54.620
And this time, Tu'er has brought
a whole group of Jing Kes with him.

30:55.880 --> 30:56.740
Your Highness,

30:57.480 --> 30:58.680
do you think we should

30:59.200 --> 31:01.160
reveal something to the Emperor?

31:05.960 --> 31:07.550
I didn't expect that you, Mr. Cao,

31:07.550 --> 31:09.810
would be so concerned about the Emperor.

31:09.930 --> 31:12.940
I'm thinking entirely of
Your Highness's interests.

31:13.400 --> 31:16.180
If Tu'er really kills the Emperor,

31:16.270 --> 31:17.880
war will break out
between our states again.

31:17.880 --> 31:18.720
By then,

31:18.880 --> 31:22.080
we won't have resources
to deal with the Empress Dowager.

31:22.400 --> 31:24.530
I was thinking the same thing earlier.

31:26.350 --> 31:28.080
But then I realized something.

31:28.350 --> 31:30.210
Since the person coming is Tu'er,

31:30.920 --> 31:31.850
with his skills,

31:32.880 --> 31:33.960
when carrying out the assassin
like Jing Ke,

31:33.960 --> 31:36.560
accidentally killing
the Empress Dowager too

31:37.960 --> 31:39.820
shouldn't be difficult, right?

31:40.410 --> 31:42.790
With no one at the helm,

31:43.160 --> 31:44.820
formidable enemies outside,

31:44.920 --> 31:46.680
and the Crown Prince still young,

31:46.680 --> 31:50.640
someone would have to serve as regent
to manage state affairs.

31:50.830 --> 31:51.710
As for the war,

31:52.030 --> 31:53.760
since we're all aware of it now,

31:53.920 --> 31:55.380
we can prepare in advance,

31:55.510 --> 31:57.350
so we won't be caught off guard

31:57.590 --> 31:59.590
by the Yan State's surprise attack.

31:59.920 --> 32:02.320
Therefore, we need not inform the Emperor.

32:03.910 --> 32:05.160
When necessary,

32:06.440 --> 32:08.990
we can even lend Tu'er a helping hand.

32:29.030 --> 32:30.860
[Ten years ago] [Emperor of Yan]

32:30.910 --> 32:33.140
[Ten years ago]

32:32.200 --> 32:33.800
Your Majesty, this is Tu'er.

32:34.510 --> 32:35.550
Un... Un...

32:36.510 --> 32:37.380
Uncle.

32:47.510 --> 32:48.240
Does it hurt?

32:48.770 --> 32:49.630
No, it doesn't.

32:55.920 --> 32:56.650
What's this?

32:57.270 --> 32:58.670
It's a Camel Bell flower.

32:59.000 --> 33:00.130
It's really pretty.

33:29.680 --> 33:30.190
Shanyi!

33:33.480 --> 33:34.210
Is it pretty?

33:36.240 --> 33:36.840
Yes, it is.

33:37.920 --> 33:39.920
I'm about to leave for the Great Xia.

33:42.000 --> 33:43.660
Has our Yan State run out of men

33:45.000 --> 33:47.130
that we have to send a woman
as an envoy?

33:47.960 --> 33:49.350
Because I'm the holy maiden

33:49.350 --> 33:50.880
chosen by the people of Yan.

33:51.350 --> 33:53.980
Naturally, I must go and dance for them.

33:55.030 --> 33:57.110
This is a dagger I made myself.

33:57.880 --> 33:59.210
Take it for protection.

34:01.200 --> 34:02.330
It's really pretty.

34:03.400 --> 34:05.600
Even engraved with Camel Bell flowers.

34:07.350 --> 34:09.020
I wanted to go with you,

34:09.840 --> 34:12.570
but Uncle insists I stay
to handle state affairs.

34:13.710 --> 34:15.510
Please be extra careful on your journey.

34:15.510 --> 34:16.250
Don't worry.

34:16.510 --> 34:18.510
I'm going for peace talks, not war.

34:18.880 --> 34:20.340
There won't be any danger.

34:20.630 --> 34:23.090
Shanyi, hurry up!
We're all waiting for you.

34:23.150 --> 34:23.610
Coming!

34:30.630 --> 34:31.170
Tu'er.

34:31.710 --> 34:33.000
Wait for me to come back.

34:33.000 --> 34:34.600
I have something to tell you.

34:38.840 --> 34:39.239
Uncle.

34:39.630 --> 34:41.230
Why hasn't Shanyi returned?

34:41.590 --> 34:42.850
She's the holy maiden.

34:42.880 --> 34:45.810
She should have returned with
the envoy delegation.

34:54.550 --> 34:55.070
Uncle.

34:57.510 --> 34:58.910
What happened to Shanyi?

34:59.480 --> 35:01.280
That Emperor of the Great Xia...

35:02.190 --> 35:04.250
He was impressed by Shanyi's dancing

35:04.760 --> 35:07.000
and actually tried to
take advantage of her

35:07.000 --> 35:08.600
right there in the main hall!

35:09.230 --> 35:09.880
Shanyi

35:11.250 --> 35:12.650
refused to be humiliated

35:12.900 --> 35:14.150
and fought back fiercely,

35:14.150 --> 35:15.510
but that Emperor...

35:17.030 --> 35:20.290
He actually killed Shanyi!

35:38.800 --> 35:40.940
Zhang San's Diary.

36:20.100 --> 36:23.850
[Rockery]

36:23.920 --> 36:25.870
[1-3 AM]

36:25.950 --> 36:33.710
[Rockery]

36:28.840 --> 36:29.400
It's her.

36:31.670 --> 36:32.430
She's here.

36:33.810 --> 36:36.030
[1-3 AM]
